#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"I'M HUNGRY! HE HIT ME! I'M BORED!\n"
"Sound familiar? \n"
"\n"
"Every family faces challenges. Learning how to solve problems together with your child can help you when you have conflict in your home. \n"
"\n"
"It also teaches your children how to solve problems on their own. This will set them up for success throughout their life. What a gift!"
msgstr ""
"NDILAMBILE! UNDIBETHILE! NDIDIKIWE!\n"
"Ivakala iqhelekile? \n"
"\n"
"Intsapho nganye zijamelene nemiceli mngeni. Ukufunda indlela yokusombulula iingxaki kunye nomntwana wakho kunokunceda xa unengxabano ekhayeni lakho.\n"
"\n"
"Ikwafundisa abantwana bakho ukuba bangayisombulula njani ngokunokwabo. Oku kuya kubamisela impumelelo ebomini babo bonke. Esinjani isipho!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tap play to hear how solving problems with your children can you and your family"
msgstr "Cofa udlala ukuva ukusombulula iingxaki kunye nabantwana bakho unako kunye nosapho lwakho"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Greetings, everyone.\n"
"\n"
"As parents, it can feel like we have to solve a million problems for our children every day: Where is my toy car? I am not going to school! Why can’t you buy me new shoes now?\n"
"\n"
"By involving our children in solving problems, they learn to find solutions more and more independently. \n"
"\n"
"Life has its challenges. If you help your child solve small problems today, you give them the skills to deal with any bigger challenges later in life."
msgstr ""
"Molweni nonke!\n"
"\n"
"Njengabazali, ingavakala ngathi kumele sisombulule izigidi zeengxaki zabantwana bethu mihla yonke. Iphi imoto yam yokudlala? Andiyi esikolweni! Kutheni ungandithengeli izihlangu ezintsha ngoku?\n"
"\n"
"Ngokubandakanya abantwana bethu ekusombululeni iingxaki, bafunda ukuzifumanela izisombululo kunye nokuzimela ngakumbi nangakumbi.\n"
"\n"
"Ubomi bunemiceli mngeni yabo. Ukuba unceda umntwana wakho akwazi ukusombulula iingxaki ezincinci namhlanje, ubanika isakhono sokumelana nayo nayiphi na imiceli mngeni emikhulu phambili phaya ebomini."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name
#.      @data.characters.f2_son_8.name
#.      @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Let’s look at an example of how you can solve problems together with your child: \n"
"@data.characters.f2_grandfather.name is concerned that @data.characters.f2_son_8.name is sleeping late every day and waking up tired because he starts his homework late. \n"
"\n"
"How could @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name handle this?"
msgstr ""
"Makhe sijonge umzekelo wokuba ungasombulula njani iingxaki kunye nomntwana wakho: \n"
"@data.characters.f2_grandfather.name uxhalabile kuba @data.characters.f2_son_8.name ulala emva kwexesha yonke imihla kwaye uvuka edininwe ngokuba uqala umsebenzi wesikolo emva kwexesha. \n"
"\n"
"Anga melana njani u @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name nalento?"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name
#.      @data.characters.f2_son_8.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**In the next story, @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name and @data.characters.f2_son_8.name use four steps to solve a problem:**\n"
"\n"
"1) 💡 KNOW IT: Talk to your child about what the problem is\n"
"2) 🔧 SOLVE IT: Think of possible solutions together\n"
"3) 🎯 TRY IT: Choose one solution to try\n"
"4) 💭 REFLECT: See if it worked. If not, try another solution"
msgstr ""
"**Kwibali elilandelayo, u@data.characters.f2_grandfather.name kunye no@data.characters.f2_son_8.name basebenzisa amanyathelo amane okusombulula ingxaki.**\n"
"\n"
"1)💡 YAZI: Thetha nomntwana wakho malunga nokuba yintoni ngxaki.\n"
"2) 🔧 YISOMBULULE: Cinga ngesisombululo esinokubakhona kunye.\n"
"3) 🎯 YIZAME: Khetha isisombuluo esinye oza kuzama ngaso.\n"
"4) 💭 CINGISISA: Jonga ukuba iyasebenza. ukuba ayisebenzi, Zama esinye isisombululo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Step 1: KNOW IT"
msgstr "Inyathelo 1: YAZI"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_son_8.name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Come on, @data.characters.f2_son_8.name, it's time to get ready for bed."
msgstr "Yiza, @data.characters.f2_son_8.name, lixesha lokulungiselela ulala."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "But I still have so much homework to do!"
msgstr "Kodwa ndisenomsebenzi omninzi wesikolo ekufuneka ndiwenze!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hmm, this is the third night in a row that you haven’t gone to bed on time because of homework."
msgstr "Hmm, Bubusuku besithathu evekini obu ungakhange ulale kwangethuba ngenxa yomsebenzi wesikolo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Step 2: SOLVE IT"
msgstr "Inyathelo 2: YISOMBULULE"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How can we make sure you get all your work done and still get to bed on time so that you get enough sleep?"
msgstr "Singaqinisekisa njani ukuba uyawenza wonke umsebenzi wakho kwaye ulale kwangethuba ukuze ulale ngokwaneleyo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Maybe I can start earlier?"
msgstr "Mhlawumbi ndingaqalisa kwangethuba?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Shall we make a rule that you start your homework half an hour after you get home from school? That way, you can finish it and have some time to eat and relax before bed, too!"
msgstr "Singakwazi ukwenza umthetho wokuba uqala umsebenzi wakho wesikolo emva kwesiqingatha seyure emva kokuba ubuyile eskolweni? Ngalo ndlela, ungakwazi ukuyigqiba kwaye ube nexesha lokutya kwaye nelokuphumla ngaphambi kokulala!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_grandfather.role_name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Okay, @data.characters.f2_grandfather.role_name."
msgstr "Kulungile, @data.characters.f2_grandfather.role_name."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Step 3: TEST IT"
msgstr "Inyathelo 3: YIVAVANYE"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "*The next day*"
msgstr "*Ngosuku olulandelayo*"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_son_8.name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f2_son_8.name, have you started your homework yet?"
msgstr "@data.characters.f2_son_8.name, sowuqalisile ngomsebenzi wakho wesikolo?"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_grandfather.role_name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I'll start now, @data.characters.f2_grandfather.role_name. Could you help me with this one problem? I was having trouble with it yesterday."
msgstr "Ndizakuqala ngoku, @data.characters.f2_grandfather.role_name Ungakwazi ukundinceda ngengxaki enye? Bendinengxaki kunye nayo izolo."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_son_8.name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Of course, @data.characters.f2_son_8.name."
msgstr "Kunjalo, @data.characters.f2_son_8.name."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Step 4: REFLECT"
msgstr "Inyathelo 4: CACISA"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_grandfather.role_name, should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Look, @data.characters.f2_grandfather.role_name, I'm ready for bed earlier tonight!"
msgstr "Jonga, @data.characters.f2_grandfather.role_name ndikulungele uyokulala kwangoko ngokuhlwa nje!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_son_8.name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Well done, @data.characters.f2_son_8.name. I’m proud that we figured that problem out together. Now you can be well-rested for tomorrow, and your homework is done!"
msgstr "Wenze kakuhle,@data.characters.f2_son_8.name Ndiyazingca ngokuba siyifumene kunye le ngxaki, Ngoku ungakwazi ukuphumla-kakuhle ukulungela ngomso, Kwaye nomsebenzi wesikolo ugqityiwe!"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name
#.      @data.characters.f2_son_8.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let’s reflect on how @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name and @data.characters.f2_son_8.name worked together to solve their problem."
msgstr "Makhe sicinge indlela u@data.characters.f2_grandfather.name kunye no@data.characters.f2_son_8.name abasebenze kunye ngayo ukusombulula ingxaki yabo."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What problem did this family have?"
msgstr "Yayiphi ingxaki olusapho belunayo?"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_son_8.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f2_son_8.name went to bed late"
msgstr "@data.characters.f2_son_8.name ulele emva kwexesha"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_son_8.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f2_son_8.name did not finish his homework"
msgstr "@data.characters.f2_son_8.name akawugqibanga umsebenzi wakhe wesikolo"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_son_8.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f2_son_8.name was tired"
msgstr "@data.characters.f2_son_8.name ebediniwe"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_son_8.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes, @data.characters.f2_son_8.name is still learning to manage his time well. These are all correct answers!"
msgstr "Ewe,@data.characters.f2_son_8.name usafunda ukuphatha ixesha lakhe kakuhle. Zonke ezi zimpendulo ezichanekileyo!"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name
#.      @data.characters.f2_son_8.name?
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What does @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name do to solve the problem together with @data.characters.f2_son_8.name?"
msgstr "Wenza ntoni u @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name ukusombulula ingxaki kunye no@data.characters.f2_son_8.name?"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_son_8.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He tells @data.characters.f2_son_8.name that he is disappointed in him for going to bed late"
msgstr "Uxelela u@data.characters.f2_son_8.name ukuba uphoxekile kuye kuba ayolala emva kwexesha"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name
#.      @data.characters.f2_son_8.name.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Try again! @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name looked for solutions together with @data.characters.f2_son_8.name. \n"
"Together, they used the four steps of problem solving: know it, solve it, try it, reflect."
msgstr ""
"Zama kwakhona! @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name ukhangele izisombululo kunye no @data.characters.f2_son_8.name. \n"
"Kunye, basebenzise amanyathelo amane okusombulula ingxaki: yazi, yisombulule, yizame, cingisisa."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_son_8.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He asks @data.characters.f2_son_8.name to help come up with solutions"
msgstr "Ucele u@data.characters.f2_son_8.name ukuba ancedise ukuza nezisombululo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"That’s right. This is the second step of problem solving (solve it) which means coming up with solutions together. \n"
"Together, they used the four steps of problem solving: know it, solve it, try it, reflect."
msgstr ""
"Kulungile. Eli linyathelo lesibini lokusombulula ingxaki (yisombulule) oku kuthetha ukuza nezisombululo kunye. \n"
"Bekunye, basebenzise amanyathelo amane okusombulula ingxaki: yazi, yisombulule, yizame, cingisisa."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_son_8.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "He gets angry with @data.characters.f2_son_8.name for not remembering to do his homework"
msgstr "Uyabanomsindo ngu@data.characters.f2_son_8.name kuba engakhumbuli ukwenza umsebenzi wakhe wesikolo"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f2_grandfather.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Try again! \n"
"\n"
"@data.characters.f2_grandfather.name stayed calm. Together, they used the four steps of problem solving: know it, solve it, try it, reflect."
msgstr ""
"Zama kwakhona! \n"
"\n"
"@data.characters.f2_grandfather.name wahlala ezolile. Kunye, basebenzise amanyathelo amane okusombulula ingxaki: yazi, yisombulule, yizame, cingisisa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When a problem comes up, take a deep breath before you respond. \n"
"\n"
"Then help your child work on the problem with you using these four steps."
msgstr ""
"Xa kuvela ingxaki, phefumla nzulu, ngaphambi kokuba uphendule. \n"
"\n"
"Emva koko nceda umntwana wakho asebenze kwingxaki kunye nawe usebenzisa lamanyathelo mane."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "KNOW IT"
msgstr "YAZI"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Put the problem into words.\n"
"\n"
"Talk to your child about what the problem is."
msgstr ""
"Yibeke ngamazwi ingxaki.\n"
"\n"
"Thetha nomtwana wakho malunga nokuba yintoni ingxaki."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "_\"I can hear you arguing because you don’t want to watch the same television programme. I know I said you both could watch TV after you’ve helped clean up after dinner, but we only have one television. How can we solve this problem?\"_"
msgstr "_\"Ndiyaniva ukuba niyaxambulisana kuba anifuni kubukela inkqubo enye kumabonakude. Ndiyayazi ukuba ndithe ningabukela umabonakude nobabini emva kokuba nincedise ukucoceni emva kwesidlo sangokuhlwa, kodwa sinomabonakude omnye nje. Singayisombulula njani le ngxaki?\"_"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SOLVE IT"
msgstr "YISOMBULULE"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Together, think of possible solutions to this problem.\n"
"What could you or your child do differently in this situation in the future?"
msgstr ""
"Kunye, cingani ngezisombululo ezinokubakho kule ngxaki.\n"
"Yintoni wena okanye umntwana wakho onokuyenza ngokwahlukileyo kule meko kwixesha elizayo?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "_\"One option is for us not to turn the television on at all. You can also take turns choosing a programme or select one you both want to watch. What do you both think?\"_"
msgstr "_''Olunye ukhetho kukuba angavuli umabonakude kwaphela. Ningatshintshana ukukhetha inkqubo okanye ukhethe enye enifuna ukuyibukela nobabini. Nicinga ntoni nobabini?\"_"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "TRY IT"
msgstr "YIZAME"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Choose one solution together.\n"
"\n"
"Try it next time you are in a similar situation, and praise your child for trying!"
msgstr ""
"Khetha isisombululo esinye kunye.\n"
"\n"
"Yizame kwixesha elilandelayo ukwimeko efanayo, kwaye umncome umntwana wakho ngokuzama oko!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"_\"Okay boys, do you remember what we said last night about the TV? Who can remember the solution we came up with?\"\n"
"\"That's right – well done for remembering! Let's try to pick a programme that you both want to watch – I can even come watch with you!\"_"
msgstr ""
"_\"Kulungile bafana, niyakhumbula ukuba sithethe ntoni phezolo ngo MABONAKUDE? Ngubani osasikhumbulayo isisombululo esize naso?\"\n"
"\"Kulungile - wenze kakuhle ukukhumbula! Masizame ukukhetha inkqubo enifuna ukuyibukela nobabini - ndingeza nam ndizokubukela kunye nani!\"_"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "REFLECT"
msgstr "Cingisisa"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "After you’ve tried it, decide with your child whether or not your solution worked."
msgstr "Emva kokuba uyizamile, yenza isigqibo nomntwana wakho ukuba isisombululo sakho sisebenzile na okanye hayi."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "What you could say"
msgstr "Yintoni onokuthi uyithethe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "After the programme ends… _“Well that was an exciting game! I never knew I liked watching soccer so much, so thank you for introducing me to something new! I think we all had fun watching that together.”_"
msgstr "Emva kokuba inkqubo iphelile... _\"Ewe Ibingumdlalo onika umdla! Zange ndiyazi ukuba ndiyakuthanda ukubukela ibhola ekhatywayo kakhulu, ngoko ke ndiyabulela ngondazisa ngento entsha! Ndicinga ukuba sonke sikonwabele ukubukela loo nto kunye.\"_"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let’s think of some common problems we could solve with our children."
msgstr "Makhe sicinge ngeengxaki eziqhelekileyo esinokuzisombulula kunye nabantwana bethu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Do you experience any of these problems at home with your children?"
msgstr "Ingaba ufumana nayiphi na kwezi ngxaki ekhaya kunye nabantwana bakho?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Too much screen time"
msgstr "Ixesha lokubukela ngokugqithisileyo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Coming home late"
msgstr "Ukubuya emva kwexesha ekhaya"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Fighting with other children"
msgstr "Ukulwa kunye nabanye abantwana"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Not sharing toys"
msgstr "Ukungabelani ngezinto zokudlala"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Talk with your child and use the steps of problem-solving together to come up with solutions that you can try out."
msgstr "Thetha nomtwana wakho kwaye nisebenzise amanyathelo okusombulula ingxaki kunye ukuze nize nezisombululo eninokwazi ukuzizama."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Your home activity is to identify a problem your child may have and practise the four steps of problem-solving together: Know It, Solve It, Try It, Reflect. \n"
"\n"
"Knowing how to solve problems is something they can use for the rest of their lives!"
msgstr ""
"Umsebenzi wakho wasekhaya kukuchonga ingxaki umntwana wakho onokuba nayo kwaye uzame amanyathelo amane okusombulula iingxaki kunye: Yazi, Yisombulule, Yizame, Cingisisa. \n"
"\n"
"Ukwazi ukuba uzisombulula njani iingxaki yinto abangayisebenzisa ubomi babo bonke!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_female_5.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hear how @data.characters.media_female_5.name and her daughter use the four steps of problem solving"
msgstr "Mamela u @data.characters.media_female_5.name kunye nentombi yakhe besebenzisa njani amanyathelo amane okusombulula ingxaki"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"I did not have a good relationship with my daughter. I was always shouting at her, and she was refusing to go to school. \n"
"\n"
"Only when I started spending One-on-One Time with her, I realised that she did not want to go to school because she was being bullied at school. We sat down and used the four steps of problem solving. We identified the problem, and figured out solutions together: “What can I do as a parent so you can attend school and feel safe?”\n"
"\n"
"We agreed I would go talk to the teacher to find a way forward. We really found the solutions together, and we are closer now."
msgstr ""
"Bendingenabo ubudlelwana obulungileyo nentombi yam. Bendisoloko ndimngxolisa kwaye ebengafuni\n"
"ukuya esikolweni. \n"
"\n"
"Xa ndandiqala ukuchitha ixesha naye lomnye nomnye, ndafumanisa ukuba akafuni ukuya esikolweni kuba exhatshazwa esikolweni. Sihleli phantsi sasebenzisa amanyathelo ayi 6 wokusombulula ingxaki. Siyibonile ingxaki, kwaye sakhangela isisombululo sisonke. \"Ndingenza ntoni njengomzali ukuze ukwazi ukuya esikolweni kwaye uzive ukhuselekile?\"\n"
"\n"
"Siye savumelana ukuba ndizothetha notitshala ukuze sizokufumana izisombululo kunye kwaye sisondelelene ngoku."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you try to solve a problem with your child this week?"
msgstr "Ungakwazi ukusombulula ingxaki kunye nomntwana wakho kuleveki?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Ewe"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think so"
msgstr "Ndicinga njalo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's great! Remember to praise them for their effort, and praise yourself, too! Well done!"
msgstr "Kulungile! Khumbula ukubancoma ngomzamo wabo, kwaye uzincome ngokunjalo! Usebenzile!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No"
msgstr "Hayi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's okay. Try to work on a simple problem with your child, before you tackle a big one together."
msgstr "Kulungile! Zama ukusebenza kwingxaki elula nomtwana wakho, ngaphambi kokuba nijongane nenkulu kunye."

